  "body": "This is a tracker to collect all issues regarding to improving lodestar error UX. Most of the times we are pretty aggressive in throwing error even if its intermittent/self resolvable and requires no user action/attention.\r\n\r\nFor such issues, an error accumulator should be used and only throw if accumulator exceeds threshold (accum resets and starts from 0 if the progress is made between consecutive tries)\r\n\r\nIssues:\r\n- [x] Block Parent Unknown https://github.com/ChainSafe/lodestar/issues/3062#issuecomment-1211457758 as raised here https://github.com/ChainSafe/lodestar/issues/3062 and https://github.com/flashbots/mev-boost/issues/157\r\n- [ ] https://github.com/ChainSafe/lodestar/issues/4348\r\n- [ ] https://github.com/ChainSafe/lodestar/issues/5938\r\n- [x] https://github.com/ChainSafe/lodestar/issues/4396\r\n-  [x] https://github.com/ChainSafe/lodestar/issues/4146\r\n-  [x] https://github.com/ChainSafe/lodestar/issues/3569\r\n-  [x] https://github.com/ChainSafe/lodestar/issues/3605\r\n-  [x] https://github.com/ChainSafe/lodestar/issues/4522\r\n-  [x] https://github.com/ChainSafe/lodestar/issues/4523\r\n-  [x] https://github.com/ChainSafe/lodestar/issues/2311\r\n-  [x] https://github.com/ChainSafe/lodestar/issues/4540\r\n-  [x] https://github.com/ChainSafe/lodestar/issues/4559",
